Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 有人來商談動畫化的事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:08.87,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻譯 妹控　小亂　小雨　印第安馬 校譯 印第安馬 後期 DK 壓制 童話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就商談的話 還是稍微早了點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人也說了只是先打個招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要對亞豆說起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓她期望過高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還是可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」的人氣這麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要畫出有趣的漫畫就一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直是抱著這種想法在創作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有一天能動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:49.21,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}夢想 夢想 夢想 夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:56.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}每次實現時 才會崩壞的 夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:01:00.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}為何 即便如此 我仍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:07.77,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}不斷尋求 繼續奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:09.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}久別重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:11.35,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}「氣氛改變了？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:14.52,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}歲月流逝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:19.26,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}「還是那個時候快樂」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:24.25,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}失去的 許多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:31.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}其實 早就覺察到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:40.42,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}繼續吶喊吧 繼續掙扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:46.77,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}不要再 用誰來作為借口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:53.19,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}還有想要傳達的話 很多 很多 很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:57.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}夢想的前路 只剩下夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:04.14,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,480)}溫泉與二選一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啊 最高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天過來的 加籐小姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北見莉莉香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是個出道的聲優
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還是個學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你在調查這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是有公司想讓「REVERSI」動畫化嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有點按耐不住心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就這樣怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是確定了能夠動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算動畫化也是以後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在最重要的是讓我們的漫畫的變得更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 這次的正月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我們第一次有空休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這月30號到下月3號準備休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說 但也沒啥事可幹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計到最後還是在家工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我計劃和香耶去蜜月後的第一次旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜月之後？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在鬼怒川3日2晚旅行之後就沒出去過？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶 她也太可憐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想時隔4年半後再故地重遊一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶也叫你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼啊  你們兩個去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是當電燈泡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無論何時都在一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是這時候你不在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會感覺怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像公司旅行那樣 去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 極樂 極樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很像老頭子 但也想不出別的形容詞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有打擾你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要問多少遍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們3人在一起才更加開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然像這樣悠閒的休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才最爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平時都那麼拚命努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才格外能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果經常來的話 就感受不到這種感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來就到吃飯時間啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好豐盛的料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們太慢了 所以我先喝起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 香耶 沒在耍酒瘋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人 今年也請多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城 一直以來也非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家秋人多謝你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不怎麼能喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝  我喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好飽 好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 慣例的乒乓球大會 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 吃了一肚子 馬上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！ 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打 我打
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香耶 打太猛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱爆了 你們兩個大男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我用左手打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 小瞧我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動之後 酒勁上頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城 不要睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}今年終於要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起看新年日出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 要開始倒計時了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 「REVERSI」的話 一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給亞豆發新年祝福短信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又是一兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆不這樣的話就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 天開始亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望今年也一帆風順
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」的人氣越來越高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城什麼願望都不許嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年第一天的日出需要許願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是應該初次參拜神社的時候許願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都會許願的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就許願
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能和香耶還有秋人的關係一直這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真城君~你如果不是美保的男朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也對真城君…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真城君能來太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 這樣很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人 香耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼開心的新年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次還要一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次美保也要一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 香耶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正準備睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我要不就在這邊睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太噁心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三的暑假我們不是每天都睡在同一屋簷下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三的暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又感覺是最近才發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時開始我們一步不停地走到今天真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9年半的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是轉瞬間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然也有艱難的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的運氣還是很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「驕傲」「努力」「運氣」中的運氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得能和秋人相遇是我最大的運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有對我說「一起畫漫畫吧」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道現在的自己在做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是找到其他的目標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該不會有「成為日本第一的漫畫家」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「和亞豆結婚什麼的」這樣巨大的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個夢想也快要實現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經近得彷彿伸手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」的話 一定可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以說些自負的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途中的醜事不當回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是多噁心的話隨便說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得漫畫和人生是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週刊漫畫就是一周
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生就是到死的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被賦予的時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟能創造出多麼美好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說絕對不能偷工減料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驕傲和運氣固然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最重要的是努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不自負嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得就是你說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還有「體力」和「精神」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後就是「毅力」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之後就要開始工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到能這麼快交稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們想留充裕的時間來創作出更好的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4號發表的第2卷已經再版了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上第1卷已經達到50萬本了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不過 「ZOMBIE☆GUN」也再版了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 第2卷還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是「REVERSI」賣的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來發展順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能追上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！就這樣迎頭趕上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然兩部都很有人氣 但是也才連載半年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這個夏天「CROW」的動畫會完結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按現狀來看 也只能在這兩部作品中選擇一部了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到觀眾群體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得同一作者的「ZOMBIE☆GUN」比較順理成章
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是按「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的展開來看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動畫劇情很快就會追上原作的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這點來看 「REVERSI」每一話的內容都很緊湊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒那麼容易追上原作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那種劇情對小孩子來說過於複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想擴大觀眾群的話 還是應該選擇我說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那種情況讓製作方調整一下就可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相田你相當推崇「REVERSI」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二郎也說過還不想動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是「REVERSI」了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他知道有動畫化的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但估計覺得一切還為時尚早所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就去問問服部的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他說OK的話 就決定選擇「REVERSI」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是要問問他有沒有意向秋天開始動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則說什麼都是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要重新問一下雄二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」動畫化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有決定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編輯長想知道你有沒有意向從秋天開始動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在「CROW」之後呢 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以理解為你想做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我稍微考慮一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有任何問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…「CROW」的動畫做了幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到7年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起長期連載
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更想創作出能讓大家接受的作品！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照亞城木君的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好在動畫開播前漫畫就已經完結了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何最好在動畫播放期間繼續連載漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是亞城木君很固執啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找不到可以接受的辦法 是無法繼續的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 一臉嚴肅的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 雖然很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不能簡單地答覆你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說這是為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的反應應該是「動畫化！太棒了！」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之 請讓我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之盡快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…算是問一下你的意願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」就暫時不動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就算為了更好地動畫化 也還是盡量往後延比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得要連載3年以上之後才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接「CROW」檔的動畫片估計…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟亞城木君說 他們肯定是希望動畫化的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從畫漫畫開始這就是他們的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼如果告訴他們動畫化的條件是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動畫播放期間一直保持連載…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果這樣導致漫畫變得無趣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把動畫開始前漫畫也許會完結的事情如實反應給上邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但這樣的話可能就失去動畫化的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想太多 在動畫化之前保持沉默就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣就太不負責任了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我一個人想破腦袋也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別著急哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒有定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上邊問我有沒有意向讓「REVERSI」接秋番
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 都說了還沒定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是問我有沒有意向而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能拒絕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們同意 事情就定下來了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做 一定要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 事情還沒到你們想的那個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}太棒啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}動畫化！ 動畫化！ 動畫化！……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 你們先冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 在動畫完結前要保持連載？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是黑惡魔和白惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修巴魯茲和拜森的對決結束後我們三人也要一起考慮後續
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方提出在動畫結束前漫畫不可以完結的條件了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 上邊雖然沒有這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是站在動畫製作公司的立場上考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方肯定希望連載能持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天開始的動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照現在的構思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修巴魯茲和拜森的對決在秋天就會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在動畫播放過程中漫畫絕對不能完結嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 並不是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果把動畫開始時漫畫會完結的計劃報告上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動畫化的計劃也許就會被取消
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不說實情直接動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也於心不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 至少在動畫完結前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 哪怕你們能連載至動畫開播一年後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來講也會輕鬆不少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 我們不能放棄這次動畫化的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在動畫開播滿一年之前 我不會讓原作完結的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣你能保證作品的質量不會下降嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」高無疑問會成為傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望拖長劇情讓作品的質量下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事不是之前才決定的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你想要動畫化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到秋天時 連載就滿一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於動畫來講 也有了相當充足的原作資源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就暫時放棄動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到作品完結
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候製作方還有動畫化的打算的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再考慮動畫化的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 好不容易有這個機會 要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拒絕這個機會我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 我可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我努力去完成原作就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是 勉強連載即便降低質量也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不會讓質量下降的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 不像你們的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 雖然我提出讓你們盡量延長連載
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想動畫化 但是絕對不能因此降低作品質量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你們一定會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木是為了我 為了我個人的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學的時候 在開始畫漫畫之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和現在正從事聲優工作的亞豆美保約定過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的作品動畫化 女主角由她來擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現了這個夢想 我們就結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想實現前不會左顧右盼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不約會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不見面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你可能會認為我們很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木邀我和他一起成為漫畫家的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然產生了這個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我下定決心要做一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木是想讓我實現這個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你們這麼拘泥於動畫化的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我反對為了我個人的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了動畫化不惜降低作品質量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像服部先生說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等連載結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候還有動畫化的邀請也為時不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼哪 不會降低質量的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在接到邀請了 只要接受就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是作品質量下降嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞豆也不希望看到這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請來了 只要坦率接受就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為亞城木夢葉想做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 連載就按你們的想法去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時完結都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人追究 責任由我來承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美好的夢想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的作品動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角由亞豆美保來演繹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能實現這個夢想就結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能從中學堅持到現在這點也非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是為了實現這個夢想 也要同意動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我支持你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太世故了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定已經丟失了這種純粹的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上頭問我想不想動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要回答想 不管怎樣都想就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 剛才服部先生來過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你們兩個幹嗎都悶不吭聲的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為香耶來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是因為香耶太可愛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個哪根筋不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 亞城木君他們也有意思做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 請務必推薦「REVERSI」動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新妻君為動畫化所畫的「ZOMBIE☆GUN」的原創NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共20話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動畫用原創NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是說動畫化還太早了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖然我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 作為亞城木粉絲的新妻君的話應該感到高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果單行本的銷量被超過了就高興不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果動畫化就有可能被超越了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 也不能阻止「REVERSI」動畫化…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說「ZOMBIE☆GUN」想動畫化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了很多次了嗎 很快就會追上原作不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就畫足夠動畫用的原創故事就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得「ZOMBIE☆GUN」動畫化為時尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我自認為動畫很快會追上原作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是新妻君 就能像這樣不斷畫出動畫用NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以動畫用的角度來處理畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」會動畫化的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為真正的第一位的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞城木君也說想從秋天開始動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他們說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是頭大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒讓你們去問作家的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來也以為「ZOMBIE☆GUN」會拒絕動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該更加慎重地確認過才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下難辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新妻君和亞城木君都幹勁十足的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩邊都希望秋天開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」「REVERSI」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這次不行 動畫化也是遲早的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「REVERSI」必須在這次動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在被「REVERSI」搶走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是問卷排名還是單行本銷量說不定都會被超過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪部作品能成為真正的招牌的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分水嶺！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的招牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天會決定選擇哪部作品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都說了那麼多遍還沒確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新妻畫動畫用的NAME的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ZOMBIE☆GUN」顯然更強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是接「CROW」的檔 所以可能性很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然決定權在編輯長手上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最好還是別抱太大希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 昨天服部先生來過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 來過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你倆為什麼都這麼垂頭喪氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊 明明有香耶在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 超可愛的香耶都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個…到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 服部先生 歡迎…
